    2. A format makes the output look nice and the MLF option
       provides a way to get the AllGender counts and
       missing unknown sex for free.
       The format is not absolutely required.

    3, The format along with completetypes gives you
       the unknown sex column for free
   ;

   * create sample data;
   Data  SexGov;
